"{    \"translations\": [        {            \"english_version\": \"Pakistan suggested a ceasefire after the US president warned that many people could die if Iran did not agree to a deal. This ceasefire with Iran might change how the world sees the US.\",            \"english_title\": \"Pakistan Suggests Ceasefire\",            \"translated_version\": \"Pakist\u00e1n sugiri\u00f3 un alto al fuego despu\u00e9s de que el presidente de EE.UU. advirti\u00f3 que muchas personas podr\u00edan morir si Ir\u00e1n no aceptaba un acuerdo. Este alto al fuego con Ir\u00e1n podr\u00eda cambiar c\u00f3mo el mundo ve a EE.UU.\",            \"translated_title\": \"Pakist\u00e1n Sugiere Alto al Fuego\"        },        {            \"english_version\": \"Kataib Hezbollah agreed to release someone on the condition that she leaves Iraq immediately. Cecile Kohler and Jacques Paris are going home after being allowed to leave the country, according to the French president.\",            \"english_title\": \"Kataib Hezbollah Releases Person\",            \"translated_version\": \"Kataib Hezbollah acord\u00f3 liberar a alguien con la condici\u00f3n de que ella salga de Irak de inmediato. Cecile Kohler y Jacques Paris van a casa despu\u00e9s de que se les permiti\u00f3 salir del pa\u00eds, seg\u00fan el presidente franc\u00e9s.\",            \"translated_title\": \"Kataib Hezbollah Libera Persona\"        },        {            \"english_version\": \"The ruling party has introduced a draft law that takes away the people's ability to elect the president.\",            \"english_title\": \"Draft Law Removes Election Power\",            \"translated_version\": \"El partido gobernante ha presentado un proyecto de ley que quita a la gente la capacidad de elegir al presidente.\",            \"translated_title\": \"Proyecto de Ley Quita Poder de Elecci\u00f3n\"        },        {            \"english_version\": \"No Israeli diplomats are in Turkey right now, and the consulate in Istanbul has been empty for over two years.\",            \"english_title\": \"No Israeli Diplomats in Turkey\",            \"translated_version\": \"No hay diplom\u00e1ticos israel\u00edes en Turqu\u00eda ahora, y el consulado en Estambul ha estado vac\u00edo por m\u00e1s de dos a\u00f1os.\",            \"translated_title\": \"No Hay Diplom\u00e1ticos Israel\u00edes en Turqu\u00eda\"        },        {            \"english_version\": \"Israel's military said they shot at a vehicle driven by a Palestinian because they thought it was a threat.\",            \"english_title\": \"Israeli Military Shoots at Vehicle\",            \"translated_version\": \"El ej\u00e9rcito de Israel dijo que dispararon a un veh\u00edculo conducido por un palestino porque pensaron que era una amenaza.\",            \"translated_title\": \"Ej\u00e9rcito Israel\u00ed Dispara a Veh\u00edculo\"        }    ]}"